text: Got food poisoning from their peppermint milk tea. Settled already and they even offered to compensate for any hospital fees but I told them that I didn't need it. I think the review should stay here for future customers, just be careful when ordering peppermint milk tea.
Nice selection of drinks. But sugar levels should be made more versatile. Snacks such as tempura chicken isn't very nice though..
Wide wide variety of drinks here! Nice place to hang with your friends too
Looks decent and should try, just opened.
